Stream type name StreamKind/String : Stream type name StreamKindID : Number of the stream (base=0) StreamKindPos : When multiple streams, number of the stream (base=1) StreamOrder : Stream order in the file, whatever is the kind of stream (base=0) Inform : Last **Inform** call ID : A ID for this stream in this file ID/String : A ID for this stream in this file UniqueID : A unique ID for this : Compression method used Format_Settings : Settings needed for decoder used CodecID : Codec ID (found in some containers) CodecID/String : Codec ID (found in some containers) CodecID/Info : Info Deprecated Codec/String : Deprecated Codec/Info : Deprecated Codec/Url : Deprecated Duration : Play time of the stream in ms Duration/String : Play time in format : XXx YYy only, YYy omited if zero
